text.div: • Include all codes defined in http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-URLScheme

name: URLScheme
title: URLScheme
description: A Universal Resource Locator (URL) is a type of telecommunications address specified as Internet standard RFC 1738 \[http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc1738.txt\]. The URL specifies the protocol and the contact point defined by that protocol for the resource.
